quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda nende tsisebele
  15,46,“Injilemwo mushironyo nomulembe”
  15,47,"Ne khulirusia amakhonye akali mubilifu biabu, ne baliba (shinga) Abananda nibekhale khubisala biobwami nibahengana"
  15,48,"Shibulibatilakhwo obuchong’e bwosi bwosi omo tawe, ne shibalirusibwamwo tawe"
  15,49,Boolela Abasumba banje mbu esie nesie Owobulesheli obunji Owetsimbabaasi muno
  15,50,Ne eshinyasio shianje nisho eshinyasio eshilulu muno
  15,51,Ne baboolele amakhuwa kabacheni ba Ibrahim
  15,52,"Olwa benjila ewuwe nibaboola mbu; “mulembe” naboola mbu : “toto efwe khubakorerwe.”"
  15,53,Nibaboola mbu; Olaria tawe efwe khukhusubisia Omusiani wa machesi amanji”
  15,54,"Naboola; “Oh! Mumboolelanga kano, nemalile okhukofula, kho ni munjila shina yamumboolelangamwo kano?”"
  15,55,Nibaboola mbu; “Toto efwe khukhuboolela khubwatoto kho sholaba mubalia abafwitsanga omwoyo tawe.”
  15,56,Naboola mbu; “Ne niwina ufwitsanga omwoyo okhurulana nende tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe halali balia abakora?”
  15,57,Naboola; “Mana shiamumbolela shindi nishina enywe Abarumwa
  15,58,Nibaboola mbu; “Efwe khurumilwe khubandu abamabii”
  15,59,Halali balia abaloonda Luti. Toto efwe khwitsa okhuhabina abo boosi
  15,60,Halali omukhasi wuwe khumalile okhulola mbu alaba mubandu balitong’a inyuma